content: Meme coins are a cryptocurrency genre loosely defined as having an exuberant online community supporting the currency’s growth. They are sometimes identified with animated character or animal meme images. During the recent cryptocurrency boom, top currencies to gain meme coin status included Dogecoin and Shiba Inu. The category extends to lesser-known currencies such as Baby Doge and Dogelon Mars.
